
Day 74 of 100-Days-Of-Code Challenge

Debugging:

Open tsconfig.json and enable "sourceMap": true.

Recompile your code to generate the .map file.

Add some logic in index.ts and set a breakpoint by clicking on a line number:

Open the debug panel and create a launch.json file, selecting Node.js.
In launch.json, add:
Start debugging by clicking "Launch Program" or pressing F5.

Use F10 to step over lines and watch variables change in the debug panel.

